Package bacci.giovanni.deunifier.DeUniFier.pipelines.unifier

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileCounter
    Standard implementation of a pipeline able to find all identitcal sequences in a file and write:
    1 - a frequency table
    2 - a file containing all unique sequences
    3 - (optional) a file containing all ids
    FileStreamCounter
    Implementation of a FileCounter.
    SequenceFileCounter
    Implementation of a FileCounter.
    TagFileCounterMod
    Implementation of a FileCounter.
